    "Similarly model generated abstracts using 20 keywords on frequent itemsets perform well over other keyword combinations.",
    "So, it concludes that abstract generation performs well when the number of keywords on frequent itemsets equals the average number of words in a sentence.The experiment results show that the novel KG ranking algorithm with all three components produces significantly higher ROUGE scores than the remaining algorithms we experienced.",
    "We also proved that the compression rate of 100 words in the final abstract has a significant involvement in obtaining a better performance in abstract generation.",
